  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and saute until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they release their moisture and start to brown.",
    "Add the chopped bok choy and cook until it wilts.",
    "Add the yuzu-kosho and tadka spice mix and stir to combine.",
    "Add the soy sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Add the ramen noodles to the pot and cook according to the package instructions.",
    "Season the noodles with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions and serve hot."
